videos.headline: D. Woolfolk run for 25 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Darnell Woolfolk run for 25 yds to the NoTex 5 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Army gets into the end zone on their 1st drive
videos.description: Darnell Woolfolk run for 5 yds for a TD

videos.headline: North Texas' Wilson goes 22 yards untouched for TD
videos.description: North Texas' Jeffrey Wilson gets the handoff and speeds downfield for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Army's Woolfork opens scoring with 5-yard TD
videos.description: Army's Darnell Woolfork runs up the gut and gets over the goal line for a 5-yard touchdown. Kicker Blake Wilson misses the extra point, giving the Black Knights a 6-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army's Woolfork opens scoring with 5-yard TD) 2016/12/27

videos.headline: Tyler Campbell runs 70 yards for Army TD
videos.description: Tyler Campbell runs 70 yards for a TD

videos.headline: North Texas with the big hit on the punt return
videos.description: Eric Keena punt for 38 yds , Rashaad Bolton returns for no gain to the Army 33

videos.headline: Tyler Campbell jukes the North Texas defender to gain extra yards
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw pass complete to Tyler Campbell for 38 yds to the NoTex 29 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Woolfork scores second TD for Army
videos.description: Darnell Woolfork extends the Army lead to 18-7 with a 1-yard touchdown in the second quarter against North Texas.

videos.headline: K. Walker run for 26 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Kell Walker run for 26 yds to the NoTex 29 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Army RB rumbles in to extend lead
videos.description: Army's Andy Davidson runs it up the gut for a six-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: A. Morris pass,to R. Bussey Jr. for 30 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Alec Morris pass complete to Rico Bussey Jr. for 30 yds to the Army 27 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: North Texas' Wilson takes screen to the house
videos.description: In the second quarter, North Texas' Jeffrey Wilson catches the screen pass and gets good blocking downfield to score a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: North Texas WR hauls in TD to narrow deficit
videos.description: North Texas QB Alec Morris finds Rico Bussey Jr. for a 27-yard touchdown, cutting Army's lead just before halftime.

videos.headline: North Texas extends their drive by using a fake punt
videos.description: Eric Keena pass complete to Kenny Buyers for 10 yds to the NoTex 43 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Andrew Tucker fights for extra yards and hurdles over the Zaxby's sign
videos.description: Andrew Tucker run for 12 yds to the Army 15 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: A. Morris pass intercepted,E. Riley return  for 3 yds
videos.description: Alec Morris pass intercepted Elijah Riley return for 3 yds to the Army 16

videos.headline: Bradshaw adds to Army's lead with 65-yard TD
videos.description: Army QB Ahmad Bradshaw fakes the handoff and splits the defense for a 65-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: North Texas recovers a fumble off a muffed punt
videos.description: Eric Keena punt for 43 yds , Malik McGue returns for a loss of 1 yard to the Army 18 Malik McGue fumbled, recovered by NoTex Kenny Buyers

videos.headline: North Texas responds with 18-yard TD
videos.description: One play after recovering a muffed punt, North Texas' Alec Morris finds Tyler Wilson in the end zone for an 18-yard touchdown, narrowing Army's lead 31-28.

videos.headline: North Texas throws interception off trick play
videos.description: Tyler Wilson pass intercepted Elijah Riley return for no gain to the Army 4

videos.headline: North Texas ties game on 37-yard field goal
videos.description: North Texas kicker Trevor Moore ties the game with 28 seconds left in the fourth quarter with a 37-yard field goal.

videos.headline: Army scores go-ahead TD on fourth-and-goal
videos.description: On fourth-and-goal in overtime, Army's Jordan Asberry gets ball and runs into the end zone for a 3-yard score.

videos.headline: Army wins by shutting down North Texas on fourth down
videos.description: After Army scores a touchdown in overtime, North Texas looks to answer but quarterback Alec Morris' pass is knocked down on fourth-and-9, giving the Black Knights a 38-31 victory.
